Package org.lfenergy.compas.sct.commons.scl.dtt

Class DataTypeTemplateAdapter

java.lang.Object
org.lfenergy.compas.sct.commons.scl.SclElementAdapter<SclRootAdapter,TDataTypeTemplates>
org.lfenergy.compas.sct.commons.scl.dtt.DataTypeTemplateAdapter
public class DataTypeTemplateAdapter extends SclElementAdapter<SclRootAdapter,TDataTypeTemplates>
A representation of the model object DataTypeTemplates.

The following features are supported:

  1. Adapter
    • Returns the value of the LNodeTypeAdapter reference object By Id
    • Returns the value of the LNodeTypeAdapter containment reference list
    • Returns the value of the DOTypeAdapter reference object By Id
    • Returns the value of the DOTypeAdapters containment reference list
    • Returns the value of the DATypeAdapter reference object By Id
    • Returns the value of the DATypeAdapter containment reference list
    • Returns the value of the EnumTypeAdapter reference object By Id
    • Returns the value of the EnumTypeAdapters containment reference list
  2. Principal functions
    • Add TPrivate under this object
    • Add TDataTypeTemplates describing the childrens TLNodeType,TDOType,TDAType,TEnumType that can be created under this object
    • Add TDataTypeTemplates describing the children TEnumType that can be created under this object
    • Add TDataTypeTemplates describing the children TLNodeType that can be created under this object
    • Add TDataTypeTemplates describing the children TDOType that can be created under this object
    • Add TDataTypeTemplates describing the children TDAType that can be created under this object
    • Returns LNodeTypeAdapter containment reference list that match DO object And DOType Id
    • Returns DOTypeAdapter object Of Type SDO By DOType Id
    • Returns DOTypeAdapter containment reference list that match DA object Of Type Enum And EnumType Id
    • Returns DATypeAdapter containment reference list that match BDA object Of Type Enum And EnumType Id
    • Returns DATypeAdapter object that match BDA object Of Type Struct By DAType Id
  3. Checklist functions
    • Compare Two TIDNaming
    • Compare Two TDataTypeTemplateAdapter's By these Private
See Also:
